Replace debug.contribution.ts with minimal stub for web-embedded

Instead of patching the 700+ line debug.contribution.ts (which conflicts
on every upstream update), create a minimal stub file that only registers
the essential services and view container. The original file is left
untouched but unreferenced (dead code, not compiled into the bundle).

The stub keeps:
- registerSingleton(IDebugService) — injected by 12+ other modules
- registerSingleton(IDebugVisualizerService) — used by visualizer consumers
- registerViewContainer — extensions contribute debug views here
- registerColors — debug color tokens used by themes

